name: Number 26: Octobypass the Dimensional Pathway
desc:
2 Level 3 monsters
At the start of the Battle Phase: You can detach 1 material from this card; during this Battle Phase, only 1 monster can attack, and its attacks become direct attacks. You can only use this effect of "Number 26: Octobypass the Dimensional Pathway" once per turn. At the end of the Damage Step, if a monster inflicted battle damage by a direct attack: Give control of that monster that attacked to the turn player's opponent.
